Class WkfTransition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axelor.db.Model

        • com.axelor.studio.db.WkfTransition

  • @Entity
public class WkfTransition
extends com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
    This object store transition information of nodes of workflow. Transition can be on button or on condition. So it will be used to generate button and actions.
